--------------------Summary----------------
eVuln ID: EV0122
Vendor: Manic Web
Software: MWGuest
Sowtware's Web Site: http://www.manicweb.co.uk/
Versions: 2.1.0
Critical Level: Harmless
Type: Cross-Site Scripting
Class: Remote
Status: Unpatched. No reply from developer(s)
PoC/Exploit: Available
